le=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">CONTOH: </span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">a. Latitude = -7.7475605 </span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">b. Longitude = 112.7221218 </span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">5. Klik CREATE QRCODE </span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">6. DOWNLOAD QRCODE DAN TEMPELKAN DI DENAH LOKASI PADA BUKU INDUK</span></span></span></span></p>\n', 0, NULL, 1, 7, 201, NULL, 1, NULL, '2024-03-01 03:38:04', NULL);
